Descendants of Dytszen [Derrick] DUYTS (Part: Dye-2)

 

The Dye family tree is one of the larger family trees on the Monroe County, Ohio History and Genealogy websites. As a single family tree it includes 16 generations and numbers about 23,000 entries. Because of its size it is difficult to present the entire family tree as a single file on the website.

To make the presentation of the Dye family tree more manageable, it has been divided into 4-parts. Each part is approximately one-fourth of the whole Dytszen [Derrick] DUYTS (Dye) family tree. The initial part begins with the ancestor, Dytszen [Derrick] DUYTS, and is identified as Dye-1. Subsequent parts are identified as Dye-2 through Dye-4 and are in consecutive order.
